<br>
That how-to for Raps by Armok helped me, mainly one component. When corssing the water, doing those little loops TOTALLY helps grouping them up. Try it out, works on the wyverns great as well. <br>
<br>
My main problem is the chances of a rez out here are very low and that's a pain because one little slipup and your raptor chum.  <p><center><table width="50%" border="2" height="74" bordercolor="#FF0000" bgcolor="#000000">
